PURPOSE:-
--------
To show the operation of IP Fragmentation for AODV under mixed 
(wired and wireless) scenario.


SCENARIO:-
---------

-------- means a wired link

-------
|     |
|     | means a wireless subnet where the nodes are directly reachable
|     |
-------

-------------
|  1   7    |
|           |
|  2     4 -|-------- 8 --------- 9
|           |  N2-2.0    N2-3.0
| 3   5   6 |
-------------
  N8-1.0

CBR is used to send 100 data segments of 2020 bytes from node 1 to node 9.


RUN:-
----
Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet default.config'.


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. default.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. default.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. default.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
4. README - This file.
